{"tid":247647,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"wide lens影景 有時人+景 大光圈重唔重要","createTime":"2017-05-18T03:22:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-18T05:14:43.000Z","uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"075bb7bb9b1b24c938e8791b35c457ff55cdd8df","tid":247647,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T03:22:17.000Z","msg":"諗緊Tokina 11-16/  EF-S 10-18mm <br />\n<br />\n「Tokina 11-16 」<br />\n優點:<br />\n叫做2.8大光圈鏡<br />\n輕<br />\n外型可靠（表裡唔成正比）<br />\n對焦速度可接受（對焦能力類似CANON 35 2冇IS個枝咁既電鑽聲）<br />\n<br />\n缺點:<br />\n對焦唔算靜<br />\n＠2.8光圈15M外所謂無限遠變曬散景<br />\n無限遠扭到最盡都係唔SHARP，好似再扭過D先SHARP，但已經最盡<br />\n＠2.8光圈無限遠連最基本SHARPNESS都唔達標<br />\n個人覺得2.8光圈完全不可用，不過用黎影星影銀河要開盡就唔知，未試<br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「EF-S 10-18」<br />\n<br />\n優點:<br />\n輕<br />\n細支<br />\n有IS<br />\n最重要:平,我14年12月買$2200,仲有張32GB卡送<br />\n行STM唔會嘈<br />\n用67MM FITLER,甩支18-135KIT個塊放落去<br />\n<br />\n缺點:<br />\n個接環係膠做<br />\n唔防水滴膠邊,不過呢個價錢就由佢<br />\n光圈幾細下,入室內要推高ISO<br />\n邊位變型,一分錢一分貨冇得咁比<br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------<br />\nFor 部1300D 平平地玩住先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但唔識 有冇人請教下<br />\n但Tokina 個個都話會有紫邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea463bafd2fd5771e3ce3f701b45847481f5ad95","tid":247647,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T04:27:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e66a4dddf69b5157454986fb5f1ae78927600155","tid":247647,"uid":26080,"l